comments: Gordon (ORL) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Bogdanovic's (UTA) drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Bogdanovic (UTA) makes incidental contact with Gordon (ORL) that does not affect his FOM during the inbounds pass.
Vucevic (ORL) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of O'Neale (UTA) and does not deliver contact.
Fournier (ORL) veers slightly into O'Neale (UTA) during his shot attempt but does not affect his ability to contest the shot attempt.
O'Neale (UTA) slides his pivot foot before the start of his dribble.
O'Neale (UTA) briefly places a resting hand on Ross (ORL) off ball, the contact does not affect his FOM.
Vucevic (ORL) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Ingles (UTA) and does not deliver contact.
Bogdanovic (UTA) establishes himself in Fournier's (ORL) path during the pick and does not deliver contact.
Mitchell (UTA) has his right hand on the side of the ball and legally maintains his dribble.
Ingles (UTA) and Fournier (ORL) engage and disengage off-ball.
Vucevic (ORL) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Ingles (UTA) and does not deliver contact.
Bogdanovic (UTA) establishes himself in Fournier's (ORL) path during the pick and does not deliver contact.
Mitchell (UTA) extends his arm and delivers contact to Gordon (ORL) during his drive that affect his defensive position.
Vucevic (ORL) is firming up and makes marginal contact with Ingles (UTA) during the screen.
Vucevic (ORL) and Ingles (UTA) engage and disengage during the rebound.
Vucevic (ORL) and O'Neale (UTA) make contact with each other during the rebound.
Fournier (ORL) commits a take foul on Ingles (UTA).
Bogdanovic (UTA) makes marginal arm contact to Fournier (ORL) during his upward shooting motion.
Fournier (ORL) makes incidental contact with Mitchell (UTA) that does not affect his FOM.
Gobert (UTA) makes contact with the shot attempt after the ball has reached it's apex.
Gordon (ORL) commits a take foul on Bogdanovic (UTA).
